From: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 17:12:33 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] feat(rfork): race seed retry with async mount fallback

After the first RFork seed lookup misses, concurrently wait for async model mount fallback resolution and retry seed lookup. Continue RFork transfer when a seed appears first, otherwise use the async mounted fallback path.

Signed-off-by: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
---
 .../model_loader/rfork/test_rfork_loader.py   |  4 +-
 .../model_loader/rfork/test_rfork_worker.py   | 47 +++++++++++++++++
 .../model_loader/rfork/rfork_loader.py        | 15 +++++-
 .../model_loader/rfork/rfork_worker.py        | 52 +++++++++++++++++++
 4 files changed, 114 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/tests/ut/model_loader/rfork/test_rfork_loader.py b/tests/ut/model_loader/rfork/test_rfork_loader.py
